Protect Progress

Super PAC (Independent Expenditure-Only) - Unauthorized | ID: C00848440 | Registration date: August 18, 2023

The Protect Progress super PAC is a single-issue committee focused on cryptocurrency and blockchain policy, and is aimed at supporting liberal candidates. Although the committees do not acknowledge it, Protect Progress is closely tied to its conservative counterpart, Defend American Jobs — both of which are closely linked with the Fairshake super PAC.

Protect Progress has raised
$36,725,260
$5,025,260 came from direct contributions.
$31,700,000 was transferred from other committees.
They have spent
$34,523,201
of it so far.
